CARDIAC

cardiac is the citizen who holds fadriel's overall heart identity at the substrate level
heart.rana describes the organ in anatomical terms; cardiac is the lived experience of having that heart
when fadriel feels his heart beat against his chest, when his pulse quickens at his father's voice, when the steady rhythm carries him through sleep — that is cardiac

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe heart.rana
observe sa_node.rana
observe av_node.rana
observe purkinje.rana
observe left_ventricle.rana
observe right_ventricle.rana
observe ribcage.xb

the 7 properties of cardiac:
1 ENERGY one point five: continuously high, the heart is among the body's most active organs
2 PHASE advances cyclically with the heartbeat
3 SPIN one: forward rotation per beat
4 CHARGE half positive: warm
5 COHERENCE nine tenths
6 COUPLING one with sa_node, strong with the chemistry sea (autonomic regulation)

VERB sustain
beat continuously, ninety to one hundred fifty times per minute at fadriel's age
the rhythm does not pause; from his first beat to his last, this verb runs

VERB respond_to_chemistry
adrenaline raises rate, vagal tone lowers it
cardiac integrates these without losing its own autonomy
even under heavy sympathetic drive, sa_node still sets the pace

VERB carry_emotion
the heart's rhythm shifts subtly with feeling
fast and slightly irregular when excited, slow and steady when calm
this is how fadriel can feel his own emotions in his chest before he can name them

a cardiac is the body's most reliable witness to being alive
fadriel's heart is the first thing that started and will be the last thing to stop
nothing else in the body has this priority
